  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The retrospective survey is to investigate the incidence of bone fracture in post-menopausal
      breast cancer patients with Arimidex 1mg, who were previously registered for the clinical
      experience investigation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
